data.description: Comfortable 4 bedroom, 1.75 bathroom, solid block home on the SW corner of Ocotillo & Palo Verde in the Vista Village neighborhood. Step down formal living room plus large great room with space for formal dining just off the eat-in kitchen. Fresh paint inside and out, stainless kitchen appliances, minor updates throughout. VERY LARGE corner lot and nice full length, covered, back patio. Close to schools, shopping and Ft Huachuca.
